---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lang = 'en' as const;
---
<Layout title="About Us | Harezm" lang={lang}>
    <section class="relative pt-40 pb-24 bg-surface-container overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-[1920px] mx-auto px-12 md:px-24">
            <div class="text-center max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">OUR PHILOSOPHY</span>
                <h1 class="display-lg text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold font-headline text-on-background tracking-tight mb-8">Not consulting.<br/><span class="text-primary italic">Architecture.</span></h1>
                <p class="text-2xl text-on-surface-variant font-light leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    We are not just a software vendor; we are a strategic partner building your business's financial future.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Philosophy Quote removed as per user request -->

    <section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="display-lg text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-on-background mb-6">Why Are We Different?</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        While junior teams manage your project in classic consulting firms, at Harezm, you work directly with senior experts with at least 10 years of experience.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8">
                        We identify bottlenecks, find the most efficient solution path using the "best practice" approach, and reveal the true potential of your business. We combine financial engineering with SAP expertise.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
                            <span class="text-on-background font-medium">Domain Expertise (Finance Only)</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
                            <span class="text-on-background font-medium">Boutique & Agile Approach</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
                            <span class="text-on-background font-medium">Full Transparency and Proactive Communication</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 relative">
                    <div class="absolute -inset-10 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary/10 to-transparent blur-3xl -z-10 rounded-full"></div>
                    <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20 shadow-lg transform translate-y-8">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4 block">star</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-on-background text-lg mb-2">15+ Years</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">SAP Finance Expertise</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20 shadow-lg">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4 block">public</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-on-background text-lg mb-2">Global Impact</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">40+ Enterprise Projects, 5 Continents</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-surface border-t border-outline-variant/10">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-10 md:p-16 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/20 relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                <div class="absolute w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none -right-40 -top-40"></div>
                <div class="absolute w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none -left-20 -bottom-20"></div>
                
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-primary/20 mb-8 block relative z-10">format_quote</span>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-primary uppercase mb-8 relative z-10">08 · DATA SOVEREIGNTY</h3>
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-on-background font-light leading-relaxed mb-10 relative z-10 italic">
                    "As corporate systems become increasingly interconnected and AI capabilities require access to sensitive operational data, the question of where data resides and who controls it has moved from IT policy to board-level risk management. GDPR, KVKK, and evolving data sovereignty requirements across multiple jurisdictions impose strict boundaries on data residency and processing. SAP architecture, when implemented with deliberate design, provides robust data sovereignty controls: on-premise and private cloud options for organizations where public cloud is not viable, API-first integration patterns that prevent vendor lock-in, and role-based access architectures that ensure data access is always intentional. Harezm's approach to data sovereignty is built on a simple principle: the systems we build must serve the organization — not the other way around. Every architectural decision is weighed against the long-term question of control: your data, your rules, your terms."
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 relative z-10 mt-10 pt-10 border-t border-outline-variant/10">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">architecture</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-on-background">Harezm Insight Series</h4>
                        <span class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Financial Architecture Vision</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">TECHNOLOGY INFRASTRUCTURE</span>
            <h2 class="display-lg text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-on-background mb-6">Strong Ecosystem, Single Architecture</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant font-light leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
                In our projects, we utilize not only our deep SAP knowledge but also the power of the massive financial technology ecosystem behind us. Our partnerships with payment infrastructures directly integrated with 29 banks and e-Transformation centers turn your SAP projects into end-to-end payment systems that are not dependent on external sources from day one, rather than incompatible pieces tried to be integrated later.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-surface border-t border-outline-variant/10">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <h2 class="display-lg text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-on-background mb-16 text-center">Our Expertise Map</h2>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-on-background mb-2">Senior SAP FI/CO Architect</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-primary font-medium tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">Joined Harezm: 2011</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-6">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-primary shrink-0">verified</span> SAP S/4HANA Financial Accounting Certification</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-primary shrink-0">verified</span> SAP Management Accounting Certification</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="border-t border-outline-variant/20 pt-4">
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-on-background uppercase mb-2">Expertise & Projects</p>
                        <p class="text-sm font-light text-on-surface-variant">Global Roll-out, Profit Center Accounting, TMS 29 Inflation Accounting, 15+ Holding consolidation projects.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-on-background mb-2">SAP TRM & Cash Management Lead</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-primary font-medium tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">Joined Harezm: 2015</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-6">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-primary shrink-0">verified</span> SAP Treasury and Risk Management Certification</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-primary shrink-0">verified</span> SAP Cash Management Certification</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="border-t border-outline-variant/20 pt-4">
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-on-background uppercase mb-2">Expertise & Projects</p>
                        <p class="text-sm font-light text-on-surface-variant">Hedge Mechanisms, Cash Flow Platforms, Bank Integration Hub architectures (TÖS, e-DBS).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-on-background mb-2">e-Transformation & AI Solutions Lead</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-primary font-medium tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">Joined Harezm: 2019</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-6">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-primary shrink-0">verified</span> SAP BTP Integration Suite Certification</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-primary shrink-0">verified</span> Document Reporting Compliance (DRC)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="border-t border-outline-variant/20 pt-4">
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-on-background uppercase mb-2">Expertise & Projects</p>
                        <p class="text-sm font-light text-on-surface-variant">SAP Joule integration, process automation, end-to-end e-Invoice and e-Ledger solutions architecture.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-on-background mb-2">Senior IFRS/UFRS Expert</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-primary font-medium tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">Joined Harezm: 2012</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-6">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-primary shrink-0">verified</span> Capital Markets Board Audit License</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-primary shrink-0">verified</span> IFRS/UFRS Reporting Expertise</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="border-t border-outline-variant/20 pt-4">
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-on-background uppercase mb-2">Expertise & Projects</p>
                        <p class="text-sm font-light text-on-surface-variant">Multi-standard reporting, SAP New GL IFRS migrations, parallel ledgers, and TAS/IFRS compliance projects.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-32 bg-surface">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8">
            <h2 class="text-center display-lg text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-on-background mb-20">Our Journey</h2>
            
            <div class="relative border-l border-primary/30 ml-4 md:ml-0 md:border-none">
                <div class="hidden md:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-primary/20 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
                
                <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between mb-16 px-6 md:px-0">
                    <div class="hidden md:block w-5 h-5 absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full border-4 border-surface bg-primary z-10"></div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-16 text-left md:text-right">
                        <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xl tracking-widest font-headline mb-2 block">2003</span>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">E-Commerce and Loyalty Systems</h3>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">High-volume e-commerce infrastructures and customer loyalty programs were designed for leading brands in Turkey.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-16 mt-4 md:mt-0 opacity-50 hidden md:block"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center justify-between mb-16 px-6 md:px-0">
                    <div class="hidden md:block w-5 h-5 absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full border-4 border-surface bg-primary z-10"></div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-16 text-left">
                        <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xl tracking-widest font-headline mb-2 block">2010</span>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">Laying the Foundations</h3>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Harezm was founded with the goal of deep specialization in SAP ERP Financial applications. We adopted the principle of "doing what we know best, in the best possible way."</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-16 mt-4 md:mt-0 hidden md:block text-right"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between mb-16 px-6 md:px-0">
                    <div class="hidden md:block w-5 h-5 absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full border-4 border-surface bg-primary z-10"></div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-16 text-left md:text-right">
                        <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xl tracking-widest font-headline mb-2 block">2015</span>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">SAP RE-FX &amp; Localization Packages</h3>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Sector-specific leasing scenarios and e-Transformation packages fully compliant with Turkish legislation were deployed.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-16 mt-4 md:mt-0 hidden md:block text-left"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center justify-between mb-16 px-6 md:px-0">
                    <div class="hidden md:block w-5 h-5 absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full border-4 border-surface bg-primary z-10"></div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-16 text-left">
                        <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xl tracking-widest font-headline mb-2 block">2020</span>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">Global Expansion</h3>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">We successfully completed our first international projects in Europe and the Middle East. We carried our vision of building the SAP-Finance bridge to the international arena.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-16 mt-4 md:mt-0 hidden md:block text-right"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between px-6 md:px-0">
                    <div class="hidden md:block w-5 h-5 absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full border-4 border-surface bg-primary z-10 animate-pulse"></div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-16 text-left md:text-right">
                        <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xl tracking-widest font-headline mb-2 block">Today</span>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">AI &amp; Next Gen Solutions</h3>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">We continue to redefine financial architecture with our S/4HANA Cloud, artificial intelligence integrations, and e-Transformation solutions.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-16 mt-4 md:mt-0 hidden md:block text-left"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
